 class='bradyblue16'>Hello World, this is BradyBunch Blue</span><span class='arialred16'>" + "\nAnd this is Arial Red<span class='bradyblack24'> All in the same textfield </span>";			}						if (event.target == greekfontset) {							greek_textfield.styleSheet = greekfontset.stylesheet;				greek_textfield.autoSize = TextFieldAutoSize.LEFT;				greek_textfield.embedFonts = true;				greek_textfield.text = "<span class='arialred16'>ίστε εκείνους που δραστήρια αναζητούν πληροφορίες σχετικά</span><span class='arialblack24'>με τα προϊόντα και τις υπηρεσίες σας ηλεκτρονικά και στείλετε τους επισκέπτες</span>";			}		}		//- PRIVATE & PROTECTED METHODS ---------------------------------------------------------------------------								//- PUBLIC & INTERNAL METHODS -----------------------------------------------------------------------------						//- EVENT HANDLERS ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------						//- GETTERS & SETTERS -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------						//- HELPERS -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------		//- END CLASS ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	}}